OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1776438666
OL,3,CTeen who murdered stepdad and dog for
OL,4,C'thrill' jailed for life
OL,6,FA former college student who stabbed
OL,7,Fhis stepfather and family dog to death
OL,8,Ffor a "thrill" has been jailed for
OL,9,Flife.
OL,11,FLogan Procter was 19 when he inflicted
OL,12,Fmore than 70 knife wounds on 57-year-
OL,13,Fold Christopher Owen at the family
OL,14,Fhome in Valley Road in Shirebrook,
OL,15,FDerbyshire, on 22 October last year.
OL,17,FHe also caused 15 stab injuries to
OL,18,Ftheir Jack Russell, Poppy, because he
OL,19,Fthought it would make him feel
OL,20,F"unique", Derby Crown Court heard.
OL,26,@|D@AOU|D@HO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1776438666
OL,3,CTeen who murdered stepdad and dog for
OL,4,C'thrill' jailed for life
OL,6,FThe defendant, now 20, had a stash of
OL,7,Fknives and Samurai swords and kept a
OL,8,Fseries of "kill lists", telling police
OL,9,Fhe "wanted to end so many lives".
OL,11,FProcter pleaded guilty to murder and
OL,12,Fwas jailed for life with a minimum
OL,13,Fterm of 20 years and 10 months.
OL,15,FSentencing Procter, who sat in the
OL,16,Fdock wearing a prison-issue grey
OL,17,Ftracksuit, Judge Shaun Smith KC said:
OL,18,F"The killing of your stepfather and
OL,19,Ffamily dog was brutal, sustained and
OL,20,Ffrenzied.
OL,26,@qD@DOUqD@`O]zD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1776438666
OL,3,CTeen who murdered stepdad and dog for
OL,4,C'thrill' jailed for life
OL,6,F"No-one foresaw the tragedy that was
OL,7,Fto unfold in terrifying events at your
OL,8,Fhome."
OL,10,FProsecutor Maryam Syed KC told the
OL,11,Fcourt that Procter had two mobile
OL,12,Fphones, adding: "Within the material
OL,13,Fextracted, there were compiled lists
OL,14,Fof various methods of killing and, in
OL,15,Fparticular, various kill lists, what
OL,16,Fthe prosecution say are kill lists,
OL,17,Fwith various names.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@FO]tD@QOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1776438666
OL,3,CTeen who murdered stepdad and dog for
OL,4,C'thrill' jailed for life
OL,6,F"There was a specific list in relation
OL,7,Fto 'home', which included 'mum' and
OL,8,Fanother family member, but top of the
OL,9,Flist was 'Chris'."
OL,11,FThe prosecutor said there was another
OL,12,Flist for "work" which named six
OL,13,Findividuals, one for "college" which
OL,14,Fincluded 14 names, and online searches
OL,15,Fon his devices related to torture and
OL,16,Fcannibalism.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@RO]tD@JOUtD@OO]uD@VOUuD@^O]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1776438666
OL,3,CTeen who murdered stepdad and dog for
OL,4,C'thrill' jailed for life
OL,6,FMs Syed said Procter called 999 with
OL,7,F"extreme calmness" after the murder,
OL,8,Fwhen he described how the dog had
OL,9,F"screamed" during the attack and
OL,10,F"explained he wanted it to be quick".
OL,12,FShe said: "One of the key phrases in
OL,13,Fthe 999 call, we say, was 'I wanted to
OL,14,Fend so many lives. I planned to go off
OL,15,Fso much further than this'."
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@RO]qD@AOUqD@JO]rD@AOUrD@dO]tD@
OL,26,AKOUwD@\O]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1776438666
OL,3,CTeen who murdered stepdad and dog for
OL,4,C'thrill' jailed for life
OL,6,FThe prosecutor added that Procter
OL,7,Freferred to carrying out the killings
OL,8,Ffor the "thrill" and that "this was
OL,9,Fone way, in killing his stepfather and
OL,10,Fthe dog, that he was good at
OL,11,Fsomething".
OL,13,FProcter described not feeling
OL,14,F"unique", the court heard, and carried
OL,15,Fout the attacks to "counteract" that.
OL,17,FHe also, during the call, described
OL,18,Fhis stepfather, who had been in his
OL,19,Flife for 10 years, as "stronger than I
OL,20,Fthought" and said he did not think "it
OL,21,Fwould go that far".
OL,26,@pD@IOUpD@PO]pD@[OUsD@JO]vD@AOUvD@HO]wD@
OL,26,ATOUwD@_O]{D@WOU|D@HO]|D@dOU}D@RO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1776438666
OL,3,CTeen who murdered stepdad and dog for
OL,4,C'thrill' jailed for life
OL,6,FIt is believed that Procter knew that
OL,7,FMr Owen's older brother had been
OL,8,Fmurdered in Dudley in 2007, for which
OL,9,Ftwo people were convicted at
OL,10,FWolverhampton Crown Court, Ms Syed
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FIn a victim impact statement,
OL,14,FProcter's mother, and the partner of
OL,15,FMr Owen, Alison Owen, wrote that her
OL,16,Fson had "never shown any form of anger
OL,17,For violence in all his life".
OL,26,@xD@IOUyD@\O]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1776438666
OL,3,CTeen who murdered stepdad and dog for
OL,4,C'thrill' jailed for life
OL,6,FShe said: "The outcome of this
OL,7,Fsituation will bring me no comfort at
OL,8,Fall because I have lost everything I
OL,9,Fhold dear to me ` a precious partner
OL,10,FChris and my precious boy Logan.
OL,12,F"Chris was kind, protective, loyal and
OL,13,Ftruly a beautiful gentleman. We should
OL,14,Fhave had so many more years together."
OL,16,FClive Stockwell KC, mitigating for
OL,17,FProcter, said he had been bullied and
OL,18,Fwas a "vulnerable young man" because
OL,19,Fof his mental health problems.
OL,26,@nD@KOUtD@AOUvD@fO]zD@GOUzD@\O]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1776438666
OL,3,CTeen who murdered stepdad and dog for
OL,4,C'thrill' jailed for life
OL,6,FMr Stockwell added: "In this case, not
OL,7,Fonly did Logan have an interest in
OL,8,Fcollecting knives, but Christopher
OL,9,FOwen had an interest in collecting
OL,10,Fknives.
OL,12,F"It was Christopher Owen that would
OL,13,Fbuy Logan knives to be collected in
OL,14,Fthe home."
OL,16,FMr Stockwell told the court:
OL,17,F"(Procter's) position to us has always
OL,18,Fbeen acknowledgement and sorrow for
OL,19,Fthe misery that he caused.
OL,26,@nD@UOUtD@AOUvD@JO]yD@AOUyD@BpmyD@Lpn
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1776438666
OL,3,CTeen who murdered stepdad and dog for
OL,4,C'thrill' jailed for life
OL,6,F"Christopher Owen was a completely
OL,7,Finnocent victim. Not for a moment does
OL,8,FLogan seek to ascribe any blame or
OL,9,Fcriticism of Mr Owen.
OL,11,F"There had been no cross words, there
OL,12,Fhad been no hostile behaviour from Mr
OL,13,FOwen, there had been no ill treatment
OL,14,Fperpetrated by Mr Owen."
OL,16,FDet Insp Kane Martin, of Derbyshire
OL,17,FPolice, said: "The murder of
OL,18,FChristopher Owen has devastated his
OL,19,Ffamily and friends and throughout this
OL,20,Finvestigation seeking the truth for
OL,21,Fthem has always been our focus.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@XO]yD@OOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1776438666
OL,3,CTeen who murdered stepdad and dog for
OL,4,C'thrill' jailed for life
OL,6,F"During the hearing they heard
OL,7,Fevidence of the brutal attack that Mr
OL,8,FOwen was subjected to ` and I want to
OL,9,Fcommend them for how they have
OL,10,Fconducted themselves both today and
OL,11,Fthroughout the investigation.
OL,13,F"What they will never know is why Mr
OL,14,FOwen was killed as, while Logan
OL,15,FProcter has taken responsibility for
OL,16,Fhis murder, he has never given a
OL,17,Freason for why he carried out the
OL,18,Fattack and it was made clear that Mr
OL,19,FOwen was an entirely innocent victim
OL,20,Fwho had done nothing to justify the
OL,21,Fattack."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/12
